<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jun 2022 11:55:30 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>美國隊長 Chris Evans 告別 iPhone 6s    「會想念 Home 鍵」</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/24/chris-evans-iphone-6s/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=chris-evans-iphone-6s</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jun 2022 11:55:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Chris Evans]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 6s]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106752</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>飾演美國隊長的 Chris Evans 於週五（24 日）在 Twitter 上發文稱「RIP iPhone  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">飾演美國隊長的 Chris Evans 於週五（24 日）在 Twitter 上發文稱「RIP iPhone 6s」，會想念 iPhone 6s 的主頁按鈕。他續指不會忘記每晚與 iPhone 6s 搏鬥，試圖將其充滿電，以及電量由 100% 滿電僅於數分鐘內跌到 15%，再完全關機的日子；並祝他的 iPhone 6s 能安息。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-19.46.04.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-19.46.04-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-19.46.04-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-19.46.04-720x900.jpg 720w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-19.46.04-768x960.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-19.46.04.jpg 978w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></a></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">RIP iPhone 6s</p><p>We had a good run. I’ll miss your home button.</p><p>I won’t miss the nightly battle of trying to get you to charge. Or your grainy pictures. Or your sudden drops from 100% battery, to 15%, to completely dead all within minutes.</p><p>It was a wild ride. Rest easy, pal.</p><p>&mdash; Chris Evans (@ChrisEvans) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisEvans/status/1540139380576231424?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 24, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Chris Evans 亦有於 Instagram 上載相同的內容，甚至更分享了正在轉移電話資料的相片，相片中除了那部與 Chris Evans 搏鬥多晚的 iPhone 6s 外，亦出現一部螢幕顯示正轉移電話資料的 iPhone 13，估計那部便是 Chris Evans 的新手機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41-694x447.png" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41-694x447.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41-1280x824.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41-768x494.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41-1536x989.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/截圖-2022-06-24-12.34.41-2048x1318.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：Chris Evans Instagram</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">iPhone 6s 於 2015 年 9 月推出，估計 Chris Evans 的 iPhone 6s 也為他服役將近 7 年。時至今日，iPhone 6s 仍支援最新的 iOS 15 作業系統，但據悉自 iOS 16 僅支援 iPhone 8 或以上的型號。換句話說，若然 Chris Evans 不換走他的 iPhone 6s，便不能更新即將推出的 iOS 16。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisEvans/status/1540139380576231424?cxt=HHwWgICxvemm1t8qAAAA">Evans Twitter</a>、<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CfK1nJxN6TD/">Instagram</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">—</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
