</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國地鐵禁手機開聲睇片，南京地鐵有女子被開「罰單」</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/24/subway-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=subway-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jun 2022 06:36:19 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106655</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>如在公共交通工具內將手機喇叭音量調至最大觀看影片或聽音樂，難免會對其他乘客做成極大滋擾。近日，南京有女子因玩手 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>如在公共交通工具內將手機喇叭音量調至最大觀看影片或聽音樂，難免會對其他乘客做成極大滋擾。近日，南京有女子因玩手機時未有調至靜音或使用耳機，並將聲音外放而被開「罰單」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1106675 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.47.21-694x501.png" alt="" width="694" height="501" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.47.21-694x501.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.47.21-1247x900.png 1247w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.47.21-768x554.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.47.21.png 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1106678 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.56.06-694x367.png" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.56.06-694x367.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.56.06-1280x677.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.56.06-768x406.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.56.06-1536x812.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-13.56.06-2048x1083.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/5748839235/Lz41lc99P?refer_flag=1001030103_">微博截圖</a>）</p><p>6 月 18 日，一條名為《女子乘地鐵手機聲音外放被開罰單》的影片被上載至微博。影片中顯示，一名女子在江蘇南京的地鐵上玩手機時將聲音外放，被剛好巡邏的地鐵工作人員看到，並處以「罰單」。實際上是次南京女子並沒有真正被罰，南京地鐵澄清其「罰單」只是為了倡導文明乘車而製作的「告知單」。</p><p>影片上載後成微博熱話，不少網民稱此為德政，建議類似的政策應在所有公共場所如公園、高鐵等地方實施，阻嚇他人於公共地方作出噪音滋擾行。</p><p>但早於 2019 年 10 月，中國交通運輸部己發布了《城市軌道交通客運組織與服務管理辦法》，要求乘客使用電子設備時不得外放聲音，運營方有權予以制止，如有乘客拒絕遵守，可向有關部門依法處理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1106656 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-11.59.40-694x302.png" alt="" width="694" height="302" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-11.59.40-694x302.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-11.59.40-1280x557.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-11.59.40-768x334.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-11.59.40-1536x669.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-11.59.40.png 2026w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1106657 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.00.40-694x172.png" alt="" width="694" height="172" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.00.40-694x172.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.00.40-1280x316.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.00.40-768x190.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.00.40-1536x380.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.00.40.png 1998w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="http://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2020/content_5480496.htm">中國人民共和國中央人文政府</a>）</p><p>隨後，各國等多地的地鐵亦實施相關規定禁止手機聲音外放的行為。雖然各地地鐵以勸阻為主，但北京與武漢相對嚴格，分別採取了「記錄個人信用不良信息」以及罰款的懲罰措施。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/784700/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E7%A6%81%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%96%8B%E8%81%B2%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%B0-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E5%BE%B7%E6%94%BF%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3">香港 01 </a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
